item.title: Prayer bpn6051 in Namibia
item.description: *(Ngamwa aruhe tji mohiti mondjuwo, kumba tuvari ongumbiro ndji no mutima-wo ndjenda ku Mukuru neraka roye okumuzemburuka Erike uriri, kutja Omunamasa, ayehe mekupe outoni mongumbiro ndji:) Mukuru wandje! Mukuru wandje Ete ovakrere wOye mbutuna oupwike kotjipara tjOye otjiyapuke, mutjo tweriyandja oveni kOve erike meyuva ndi eyapuke. Ete twa worongana mo mbongarero indji yOmbepo, twa wana momitima nomo meripura wetu, nombango yetu matuvanga okutwara embo rOye kovahindwa wOye. Mukuru wetu noMuhona wetu!
